description: Officials now say 1,561 people died from the disease in April - not 639 as initially announced.
title: Moscow more than doubles city's Covid-19 death toll
title_page: Moscow more than doubles city's Covid-19 death toll - BBC News
maintext: This new methodology is likely to mean the death toll will increase across the country, although Moscow was the epicentre of the epidemic for many weeks, the BBC's Sarah Rainsford reports.
